  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/67e69ff678bee75f2db964f95269470c.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/44b4671b6f95a59914f9d0d4e274b098.poster.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/44b4671b6f95a59914f9d0d4e274b098.webm?t=1749033540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/9222d2e1f05806d5e26c852b759022f9.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keiko lives in a small countryside village named Cocco. Here she attends the local agricultural university.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This university is very strict, and she is asked by a professor to help get some troublesome students to stop skipping classes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, Keiko is socially awkward, and needs to learn how to interact with others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Japanese country village</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Keiko become more self-confident</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/67e69ff678bee75f2db964f95269470c.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/44b4671b6f95a59914f9d0d4e274b098.poster.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/44b4671b6f95a59914f9d0d4e274b098.webm?t=1749033540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1065940/extras/9222d2e1f05806d5e26c852b759022f9.avif?t=1749033540\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keiko lives in a small countryside village named Cocco. Here she attends the local agricultural university.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This university is very strict, and she is asked by a professor to help get some troublesome students to stop skipping classes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, Keiko is socially awkward, and needs to learn how to interact with others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Japanese country village</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Keiko become more self-confident</p></li></ul>",
